</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-bwrGHU cpUCet pf-2604_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-hUTmjW ewCXhB pf-2590_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="b6ce840e-4ed0-4749-9533-a5065a2aac44" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Changing attitudes through action
