</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-2183_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-2182_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-2127_">Organisations making a difference</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-2130_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-0fc37f54-efa3-480f-a0c0-242a77282264"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Now that we've explored why Race Equality Week is so important let's recognise the organisations that are actively supporting this vital initiative:
