</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-2650_"><strong>United Nations</strong> - On a global scale, the United Nations plays a pivotal role in promoting racial equality and awareness. Their various agencies and programs support initiatives worldwide.
