ness.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-123_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-124_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-125_">Conclusion</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/three-happy-gen-z-girls-wear-underwear-looking-at-2023-11-27-05-35-33-utc.jpg?v=1707828885" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/three-happy-gen-z-girls-wear-underwear-looking-at-2023-11-27-05-35-33-utc.jpg?v=1707828885 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/three-happy-gen-z-girls-wear-underwear-looking-at-2023-11-27-05-35-33-utc_1500x.jpg?v=1707828885 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/three-happy-gen-z-girls-wear-underwear-looking-at-2023-11-27-05-35-33-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1707828885 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/three-happy-gen-z-girls-wear-underwear-looking-at-2023-11-27-05-35-33-utc_500x.jpg?v=1707828885 320w" width="2271" height="1514" alt="ComplyPlus training: Empowering organisations to combat racism - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="ComplyPlus training: Empowering organisations to combat racism - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-knuQPt boqfLv pf-127_"/><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-128_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by insta_photos via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-130_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Race Equality Week is not just a week on the calendar; it's a vital catalyst for change. It unites people from diverse backgrounds and organisations from across the globe in the pursuit of a world where racial equality is not just an aspiration but a reality. With the support of these organisations and the commitment of individuals like you, we can turn the vision of a more equitable society into a powerf